{"tid":106062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［忽然左膠］奧巴馬阻精神病人擁槍法規 共和黨控眾議院 表決廢除","createTime":"2017-02-03T10:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T11:36:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ebeca8df8fbc63f894a0da376eee748c0c31f85","tid":106062,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"反對槍械管制的美國總統特朗普上台後，眾議院周四通過廢除一項前總統奧巴馬時期的槍管法規，該法規目的是禁止精神病人擁槍，是共和黨首個推翻奧巴馬槍管法的行動。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬任內曾加強槍械管制，但受到國會極力反對，他2015年推出多項行政措施，包括徹底檢查全國即時犯罪背景調查系統（NICS），被社會安全局（SSA）視為有精神病的人，要納入有關系統內，旨在禁止精神病人持有槍械。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬去年12月頒布這項法規，並且於1月18日，即總統特朗普入主白宮前2天生效，但這項法規周四被共和黨主導的眾議院，以壓倒性235票對180票廢除，法案將交由參議院再表決。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院司法委員會主席古德利特（Bob Goodlatte）表決後發表聲明說：「這項奧巴馬政府的法規具有歧視意味，也剝奪守法公民的憲法權利。」他續指：「沒有證據顯示，從社會安全局領取身心障礙津貼的人，會對公共安全造成威脅。」"},{"pid":"ebf30f74927f3f0fb85293f2cf551d6c789bbd34","tid":106062,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d7c7275e1acea096e911079c2571b68ce96346","tid":106062,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"Errrrrrrr 痴線既真係唔比佢有槍好喎⋯⋯"},{"pid":"bc9a66d9b587cc07419519d1bd1617f57aa29c45","tid":106062,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:23:17.000Z","msg":"越來越正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff75dc238c74e030e3b0ef7efe4b7f732f6c8ed","tid":106062,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:26:44.000Z","msg":"痴線佬真係要瘋狂掃射慶祝一番"},{"pid":"5904e19733bfb992c0e32b0dd110c65c9f96b6f2","tid":106062,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc4797a452572e5d7427960400e1d81e516435b","tid":106062,"uid":53677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7636cd7ab40ce5a60b67db1111c17fdf0f97e8c8","tid":106062,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"beb01a9976e02790f0b00ab1df9a453ef3e5c5b3","tid":106062,"uid":44071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:33:44.000Z","msg":"咁算左膠定係右膠？<br />\n<br />\n精神病人平權應該算左膠<br />\n開放持有槍械應該算右膠<br />\n<br />\n好混亂"},{"pid":"74ca7883a0ffa6f2bac7d3baecb2a262c9d8a2fd","tid":106062,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁算左膠定係右膠？<br />\n<br />\n精神病人平權應該算左膠<br />\n開放持有槍械應該算右膠<br />\n<br />\n好混亂</blockquote><br />\n左右balance返  所以係中膠"},{"pid":"d6ffcd64e7db7e75c5169084c4a61b94905b122c","tid":106062,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁特朗普可以有核彈<br />\n<br />\n美國精神病人都應該可以有槍既😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}